rows.label: qst102106_msg0002
rows.name:
This is just a formality, but...
are you sure you got them all?

rows.label: qst102106_msg0101
rows.name: I will take you at your word.

rows.label: qst102106_msg0152
rows.name:
So Juddit got less,
and Arthem got more.

rows.label: qst102106_msg0153
rows.name:
The numbers seem to add up
at least, but...

rows.label: qst102106_msg0201
rows.name:
More of those Spike Urchon
have appeared near the village.

rows.label: qst102106_msg0202
rows.name:
I don't know if it's because someone
didn't do their job...or they bred more
than we anticipated...

rows.label: qst102106_msg0204
rows.name:
We'll look into the reason later.
For now, go and cull the herd!
